Description:
GREAT ENTRY PRICE UNIT RIGHT IN THE HEART OF DOCKLANDS!
This stylish one bedroom apartment is located in the much sought after "Montage" low rise apartment complex. Position is perfect with landscaped gardens and a park at your front door.
Offering one generous size bedroom with a BIR and stylish bathroom, hostess style kitchen with stainless steel appliances and stone bench tops, spacious open plan living/dining area opening onto the terrace and a/c-cooling & heating to complete this fantastic package.
The location itself is ideal, with free trams just around the corner, banks, grocery shopping, eateries, cafes, and speciality shops all in close proximity. Etihad Stadium is also within walking distance, along with Harbour Town Shopping centre, and Southern Cross Station.
Currently leased out at $420 per week unfurnished, this is a great return on investment!

Description:
EXCITING ENTRY LEVEL OPPORTUNITY - MUST BE SOLD
An exciting entry level opportunity awaits in the new and chic M Docklands Complex on Latrobe Street, offering a beautiful, like new apartment with remarkable styling and finishes. Previously returning approximately 6.7%, this property is perfect for owner/occupiers and investors alike.
The open living room has plenty of natural light, and views of Etihad Stadium and the CBD presented by floor to ceiling windows. The kitchen includes a stone bench-top, glass splash-back, concealed dishwasher, Bosch oven and cook-top, concealed fridge, and Euro laundry. The bedroom comes with mirrored BIRs, whilst the strikingly designed bathroom features timber finishes, black fixtures, and subway tiling in the shower, which includes a rain-shower head. Rounding out this neat apartment is split system heating/cooling, secure car park, and secure swipe and video intercom entry.
Typical of modern apartment living residents enjoy the use of the complex's gym and heated outdoor swimming pool. In addition to these amenities, residents can take advantage of Peppers Privileges such as home delivery from the Momami Restaurant.
Located in the free tram zone, and only minutes from Southern Cross Station, this inner city pad is perfectly positioned with world class shopping, and an array of waterside restaurants and bars on its doorstep. Book an inspection today.

Description:
Dynamic Corner Offering in Yarra’s Edge
Graced with an enviable corner position, astounding quality, river views, and an abundance of space to relax both inside and out, this three bedroom, two bathroom Yarra’s Edge apartment is one of the most coveted residences in the Yarra Point building.
A picturesque parkside location, 142 sqm (approx.) of fantastic space, and exquisite style throughout is just the beginning for this 10th floor retreat. Full height windows surround the generous lounge and dining zones and allow for stunning natural light through these everyday living areas. Also included in this central hub is a stone-featured kitchen enjoying an island bench for quick meals and stainless steel Miele appliances.
The master bedroom has impeccable space as well as access to its own balcony, large built-in robe and elegant ensuite with dual vanity is also part of the master retreat. Other apartment extras include a large semi-enclosed balcony with Yarra River views, other bedrooms complete with BIRs, classy main bathroom, concealed laundry, ducted heating and cooling, secure intercom entry, two secure car spaces with over bonnet storage, and access to RekDek facilities which include a gym, pool, spa, steam room and sauna.
South Wharf Promenade restaurants, bars, and eateries are moments by foot and include Bangpop, The General Assembly, West Village NYC, Common Man, and The Boatbuilders Yard just to name a few. Also enjoy a location near DFO shops, Polly Woodside, DFO shopping, Port Melbourne attractions, Crown Casino, trams and Southern Cross Station.

Description:
Your Investment Quest Stops Here!
Positioned in the fantastic Quest Docklands Serviced Apartments and offering a hassle free investment opportunity for anyone wanting a piece of the Docklands pie, this fully-furnished one bedroom apartment is one to seriously consider opposite Etihad Stadium.
Quest Docklands is an outstanding complex with some of the best management in the area. The building enjoys an incredibly high occupancy rate, while investors will love the $2100 per month (approx.) rental returns that this apartment brings in. The outgoings for this building are also very low.
The apartment itself is modern and relaxed, and offers comfortable living and meals with great light, stylish tiled kitchen with stainless steel appliances, bedroom with built-in robe and reverse cycle cooling, sleek bathroom with a European laundry, balcony with views out to Bourke Street, and ducted heating and cooling. Residents will also have access to the neighbouring gym in Victoria Point.
Enjoy all the best that the Stadium, Batman’s Hill and Victoria Harbour precincts have to offer, where you’re moments to relaxed local cafes and eateries, Docklands Park, The Hub @ Docklands, Victoria Harbour Promenade, trams, and Southern Cross Station.
Please contact Thomas Tregonning on 0413 317 304 to arrange an exclusive viewing.

Description:
ATTENTION FIRST HOME BUYERS & INVESTORS!
WELCOME TO THE QUAYS!
Looking to invest or owner occupy? Look no further! This stunning one bedroom apartment is situated in The Quays (South Tower) development where you can sit back, relax and enjoy the bright and fresh central living zone that opens up to a North facing balcony with impressive views!
Features include:
- Spacious open plan living and dining area,
- Galley style kitchen with integrated fridge, stone bench, glass splashback and stainless steel appliances,
- Generous bedroom with floor to ceiling windows, built-in robes and a study nook,
- Lavish central bathroom with concealed European laundry,
- Ample storage space throughout,
- Split system air conditioning and heating,
- Security entrance, and
- City views.
Luxurious 5 star amenities include:
- Indoor swimming pool,
- Gym, spa and sauna,
- Private lounge,
- Library and reading room,
- Business centre and board room,
- Rooftop garden with BBQ facilities, and
- A tennis court overlooking the city skyline.
Conveniently positioned in Docklands' lively NewQuay precinct, you are situated within walking distance to trams (free tram zone), waterfront restaurants, Harbour Town shopping, Etihad Stadium, Southern Cross train station and Melbourne's CBD.
Currently leased at $1695 per calendar month, this ready-made investment is PERFECT for the savvy investor, or an ideal place to call home right in the heart of Docklands.

Description:
Bright Docklands One Bedder
Whether adding to your portfolio or taking your first step on the property ladder, this smart one bedroom apartment in the low-rise Mariner Complex should be at the top of your list, with low body corp fees and expected returns of over 6%.
Comprised of an open plan kitchen/living area, with a stylish kitchen featuring timber veneer cabinets and stainless steel appliances, the north east facing, sun drenched living area opens up onto a balcony with an impressive view of the Melbourne Star. Enjoying a premier Docklands address in the highly sought-after Yarra's Edge development, this smart riverside apartment presents modern designer living at its best. Set on Level Four of the low-rise 'Yarra Point' security building, it is defined by a north facing open plan layout with far-reaching views of the CBD/Southbank skyline plus a covered alfresco area that is ideal for entertaining. Appointed with effortless style, this superb property boasts direct park frontage and has a ground floor convenience store. * Well maintained building with intercom and an internal lift

Description:
City Views in the Heart of the Docklands!
Enjoying an enormous floorplan and wonderfully appointed interiors, this one bedroom + study apartment has many exceptional highlights including superb views and a spacious undercover balcony. Located in the heart of the Docklands only a 5 minute walk to the city, youre also close to Bourke Street cafes, Etihad Stadium, Docklands Park, Capital City Trail and local trams.
Accommodation: Graced with an immaculate presentation and a truly versatile layout, this impressive apartment promises open plan lounge and dining with plenty of space, flexible study area or potential second bedroom just off the entry, stone kitchen with quality stainless steel appliances, generous covered balcony which covers all your outdoor needs, bedroom with a built-in robe and study nook/small retreat, and bathroom featuring a concealed laundry.
Features: Secure car space, storage cage, ducted heating and cooling, secure intercom, on-site building manager, gym and concierge services

This impressive well maintained apartment allows you to enjoy views of the swimming pool below and rec BBQ area all in an ideal location allowing you immediate access to Southbank and Melbourne's CBD by foot or on one of the many trams in the Free Tram Zone at your doorstep.
Features include:
- Galley style kitchen with dishwasher and gas cooking,

Description:
Riverside Resplendence in the Coveted Yarra’s Edge
Expansive lounge and dining space, stunning views of the neighbouring Yarra River, and light-filled and stylish living are the hallmarks of this exceptional two bedroom apartment positioned in the T5 complex in Yarra’s Edge.
You’ll be instantly struck by the tremendous natural light and brilliant marina views of this 3rd floor dwelling. Floor-to-ceiling windows allows you to enjoy the relaxing vistas from the spacious and separate living and dining zones, with the dining area adjoined by a luxury kitchen equipped with a glass splashback, black stone benchtops, and stainless steel Miele appliances.
The main bedroom is generous in size and offers built-in robe storage, while the 2nd bedroom has versatility and could also be a study or home office. The large undercover balcony terrace covers all your alfresco bases, meanwhile other extras include a quality bathroom with European laundry, quality timber floors, ducted heating and cooling, intercom entry, storage cage, secure car space, and access to heated pool, spa, sauna, and gym.
Location wise, you have the Mad Duck Café, Downtown Docklands restaurant, and Lorimer Gallery right at your doorstep. You’re also a short walk to great eateries on South Wharf promenade which includes Meat Market, Bangpop, and Munich Brauhaus, while just over the Webb Bridge is an array of great attractions in the Victoria Harbour precinct.

Description:
SMART DOCKLANDS ONE BEDDER
Whether adding to your portfolio or taking your first step on the property ladder, this smart one bedroom apartment in the low-rise Mariner Complex should be at the top of your list, with low body corp fees and expected returns of close to 6%.
Comprised of an open plan kitchen/living area, with a stylish kitchen featuring timber veneer cabinets and stainless steel appliances, the north facing, sun drenched living area opens up onto a balcony with an impressive view of the Melbourne Star. The bedroom comes with mirrored built-in-robes, and the modern bathroom has a large shower, clever storage, and Euro-laundry.
Split system heating & cooling, and secure swipe & intercom entry complete this well laid out Docklands pad. With plenty of on street parking at nearby Barassi Park, bike storage, public transport, Harbour Town shopping, and an array of waterside restaurants and bars on your doorstep, this apartment is perfectly situated only minutes from the CBD and CityLink.
